Upgrade for AWP_MAP_css

Added support for 64 players (hopefully this eliminates getting stuck in another player at spawn, if not: duck and jump really fast a few times and you'll pop out.

Added 3D Skybox

Added Kewl Skewl buildings behind spawns so people wouldnt TK if they faced the wrong way.

Fixed a glitch that would mess up the lighting on any other map played after(ohh come on, you dont want to play another map anyway).

Added new walls

Thanks to CSBanana for hosting my maps.
